short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A free TikTok calculator for influencers and brands to negotiate ad rates.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Influencer Marketing Hub’s TikTok Money Calculator lets you work out the estimated earnings that you’ve made with your TikTok account(s). TikTokkers can use it to find out if they have enough followers and engagement to make money as an influencer, while brands can refer to it as a guide when negotiating rates. Note that it’s not an official TikTok tool and has not been designed for Douyin.
